{"data":[{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"0_1625738838.865215","card_id":"Q_470365349","target":{"id":470365349,"title":"如何看待「旅顺博物馆」官方回应网红「党妹」穿日式洛丽塔裙跳舞？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/470365349","type":"question","created":1625538982,"answer_count":2534,"follower_count":9264,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[285,411,99918,178649,209618],"comment_count":379,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，辽宁大连。一名粉丝数百万的网红“党妹”与朋友穿洛丽塔裙，在旅顺博物馆门口跳日系宅舞。众多网友称其在曾遭日军屠杀的旅顺穿日式洛丽塔服装跳日系宅舞非常不妥。4日，该网红致歉称，选景时忽略了旅顺博物馆在艺术文化和历史方面的含义。5日，旅顺口区政府工作人员表示，目前正在联系该网红进行调查。旅顺口官方回应网红穿日式洛丽塔裙在博物馆门口跳舞 - 封面新闻"},"attached_info":"CkAI+dvUlc7x+pp2EAMaCDY2ODA1MTU1IKaDj4cGMPsCOLBIQAByCTQ3MDM2NTM0OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"3792 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3d1764c88a8d802991cef04aa644841d_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"1_1625738838.865955","card_id":"Q_470753814","target":{"id":470753814,"title":"如何看待湘潭大学空间站舱外服设计被湖南大学占为己有？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/470753814","type":"question","created":1625666683,"answer_count":1003,"follower_count":4155,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[12849,24600,116634,725085,743630],"comment_count":107,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"​“神舟十二”成功发射 多项湘大设计将为航天员提供“贴心服务”骄傲！湖大设计，成功出舱！"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+dvUlc7x+pp2EAMaCDY2ODkxNDcyIPvolocGMGs4uyBAAXIJNDcwNzUzODE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"2751 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a43430db1b4460fb09f4d484e64ebef8_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1625738838.8665588","card_id":"Q_47